  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0db0\u0db8\u0dca\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rakna Security Lanka Company to Dhammika Perera",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has issued a special gazette placing Rakna Security Lanka Company which was under the Ministry of Defense under the Investment Promotion Minister Dhammika Perera.",
        "In addition to this, the two institutions, Selandiva Investment Limited and Hotel Developers (Lanka) Limited, which were under the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing, have been added to the Ministry of Investment Promotion under Mr. Dhammika Perera."
      ],
